TY  - JOUR
AB  - The Institut f&#xfc;r Konjunkturforschung was established in Berlin in 1925 for the purpose of analyzing and interpreting current economic data. Through its official connection with the central statistical office for the Reich, the Reichsbank, the Federal Railway Company and other large public and private organizations, this Institute has access to material which makes its weekly, monthly and interim publications of scientific importance.
